data.description: Effortless Uptown living! Le Parc Chateau is a serene condominium community nestled in the vibrant heart of Bankers Hill, mere blocks from everything the neighborhood has to offer. You will love the soaring ceilings, wood floors in the living spaces, ambient fireplace, and a private balcony overlooking the community’s pool. The expansive primary bedroom provides direct access to the balcony, ensuite bathroom with a renovated walk-in shower and dual vanity and includes a dedicated nook area perfectly suited for your home office needs. Plus a large second bedroom, recessed lighting throughout, plenty of storage, kitchen with eat-at bar, and two parking spaces. Close to iconic Balboa Park, San Diego Zoo and Hillcrest’s exciting nightlife, enjoy the lifestyle amenities of one of San Diego’s most dynamic areasLe Parc Chateau is a peaceful mid-rise condominium community situated in Bankers Hill, one of San Diego's most sought-after neighborhoods. With its tree-lined streets, charming boutiques, and eclectic dining scene, Bankers Hill and the larger swath of Hillcrest offers a unique blend of urban excitement and a welcoming community atmosphere. From this prime location, you'll have easy access to the bustling energy of downtown San Diego, Balboa Park's cultural treasures, and the world-famous San Diego Zoo, all just moments away. Easy access to most major freeways also makes community a breeze. As a gated community, residents enjoy a sense of relaxation and privacy that is unparalleled Uptown. A host of amenities include a pool, spa, and community room.
